@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ibgyst(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.90)) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.34) - 0.41))
    v2 = ((0.93 + 0.08) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.99 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v2 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.24) / 0.21))
    tmp = ((v1 - wp.abs(v2 + 0.90)) / 0.86)
    v1 = wp.cos(v2)
    v0 = (0.32 - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.28) * 0.79))
    data[tid] = v0
